                ],
                "institute": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Iron-filtered beam facility at the NBS reactor.",
                " Well-collimated l-cm-diameter beam with an intensity",
                " of 5E+5 n/(cm**2 s)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "99% of the beam composed of 25-keV neutrons and the",
                " remaining 1% made up of contaminants at 82, 137",
                " and 270 KeV. No thermal-neutron contaminant found."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "80 microg/cm2 (0.3 microns) of 6LiF with 3-cm2",
                " circular area mounted by evaporation on the front face",
                " of the Silicon surface-barrier detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Proton-recoil spectrometer used to measure spectrum of",
                " neutron beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "After determination of the background, the numbers of",
                " tritons and alphas were estimated for each of the 2pi",
                " measurements and normalized to the average number of",
                " particles observed in the forward and backward",
                " distributions. This was done under the assumption",
                " that, to the first approximation, tritons and alphas",
                " are emitted in opposite directions in the laboratory",
                " system.",
                "From the number of tritons and alphas emitted in each",
                " of the experimental conditions were determined the",
                " degree of asymmetry involved in each case:",
                " forward-to-backward 0 deg and 45 deg 2pi asymmetry,",
                " forward-to-backward 0 deg ~0.6pi (45 deg cone)",
                " asymmetry, defined as the ratio of the number of",
                " tritons in this directions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "From the experimental results a coarse-grided angular",
                " distribution obtaibed and presented in graphical form",
                " for both the lab and the center-of-mass system."
              ]
            }
          ],
